high_descs: Turn right then turn left and go just past the table then turn left then right and head to the coffee maker on the counter
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker
Turn right then turn right again and go past the table then turn right and go the wall, then turn left and go to the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave then take the mug out of the microwave
Turn left and go to the stove then turn right to face the toaster
Put the mug in the cupboard that is to the upper left of the toaster
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug into a cupboard

high_descs: Go to the coffee maker at the other end of the room
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker
Move around the kitchen island to go to the microwave
Open the microwave, put the mug inside it, turn on the microwave for a few seconds, take the mug out, and close the microwave
Turn to your left, move forward, and turn right to face counter with a toaster
Put the mug on the counter
anns.task_desc: To place a heated mug on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the coffee maker next to the sink straight ahead.
Grab the mug on the coffee maker.
Turn right and walk around the island to reach the microwave to your right.
Place the mug into the microwave, heat it and remove it.
Turn left, walk to the toaster on the counter to your right and look up to the cabinet to your left.
Place the warm mug into the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm mug into the cabinet.
